    },
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "content": "Leo introduces his cherished special box of masks. Each vibrant mask possesses the unique ability to help him express precisely how he is feeling inside right now. It makes learning about feelings truly magical!",
      "source_page_number": 1,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_001.jpg",
        "filename": "page_001.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
