        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 2,
      "content": "Leo notes that happiness blossoms through friendship or seeing warm sunshine. When Leo enjoys time with his friends, he remembers the pure delight found in simple moments. The Yellow Mask says: \"I feel happy when I play with my friends or see the warm sunshine.\"",
      "source_page_number": 2,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_002.jpg",
        "filename": "page_002.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
