        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 3,
      "content": "Sometimes sadness arrives gently like twilight, Leo observes. The Blue Mask teaches that feeling down is perfectly acceptable; perhaps a big hug can help you when your favorite toy breaks. \"I feel sad when my favorite toy breaks or when I need a big hug.\"",
      "source_page_number": 3,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_003.jpg",
        "filename": "page_003.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
