        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 4,
      "content": "When things seem unfair, anger may flare up strongly, Leo learns. The Red Mask helps him safely acknowledge that powerful feeling within himself. He shows us: \"I feel angry when things are not fair or when I have to stop playing my favorite game.\"",
      "source_page_number": 4,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_004.jpg",
        "filename": "page_004.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
