        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 5,
      "content": "When loud noises happen, the Purple Mask gently signals fear. Leo knows feeling worried about darkness or storms is completely natural and understandable for all. The mask states: \"I feel scared of loud noises or when the lights go out at night.\"",
      "source_page_number": 5,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_005.jpg",
        "filename": "page_005.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
        "path": "voices/book_level_5/page_005.mp3",
