        "provider": "kokoro",
        "language": "en",
        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 8,
      "content": "Leo always remembers this truth: every single feeling is important and okay to experience. Whether it is the red mask, blue mask, or yellow mask, understanding these emotions means they are a vital part of who you truly are.",
      "source_page_number": 8,
